AWSTemplateFormatVersion: '2010-09-09'
                Outputs:
                    NodeGroup:
                        Value: !Ref NodeGroup
                Resources:
                    NodeGroup:
                        Type: AWS::AutoScaling::AutoScalingGroup
                        Properties:
                          DesiredCapacity: 2
                          LaunchConfigurationName: example-subnet-tags-nodeLaunchConfiguration-093938e
                          MinSize: 1
                          MaxSize: 2
                          VPCZoneIdentifier: ["subnet-04304ca5940ada707","subnet-05dc85e60a2d4e7d6","subnet-0c0d7ac09ebaff625"]
                          Tags:
                          
                          - Key: Name
                            Value: example-subnet-tags-eksCluster-6e9e935-worker
                            PropagateAtLaunch: 'true'
                          - Key: kubernetes.io/cluster/example-subnet-tags-eksCluster-6e9e935
                            Value: owned
                            PropagateAtLaunch: 'true'
                        UpdatePolicy:
                          AutoScalingRollingUpdate:
                            MinInstancesInService: '1'
                            MaxBatchSize: '1'
